      <title>美国银行扩大财富管理客户的加密货币访问范围</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-expands-crypto-access-wealth-management-clients-2025-12-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行周四表示，从下个月开始，美国银行将开始允许其财富顾问在客户投资组合中推荐加密货币配置，这对于数字资产行业来说是一个具有里程碑意义的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-expands-crypto-access-wealth-management-clients-2025-12-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Dec 2025 19:15:29 GMT</pubDate>
