      <title>英国推出快速许可制度以促进金融科技增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/britain-unveils-fast-track-licensing-boost-fintech-growth-2025-12-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政部周四表示，将为金融服务初创企业推出快速许可制度，允许它们在寻求全面授权的同时启动和运营，这是削减繁文缛节和促进经济增长的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/britain-unveils-fast-track-licensing-boost-fintech-growth-2025-12-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Dec 2025 16:51:27 GMT</pubDate>
